      "step_index": 3,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "### Structural alerts relative to hERG\n- **hERG-favoring pattern:** \u201cbasic center + two hydrophobic/aromatic flanks\u201d is partially present (two aromatics + a potentially protonatable N).\n- **Anti-hERG elements:** **N-oxide** and multiple heteroatoms can reduce effective hydrophobic binding and reduce the fraction of a \u201cclean\u201d cationic amphiphile.",
