      "content": "### Hydrophobic/aromatic flanking domains\n- The molecule has **substantial aromatic/lipophilic surface** (phenyl + substituted phenyl ether, plus a second aromatic ring).\n- This supports **\u03c0\u2013\u03c0 / hydrophobic interactions** with the hERG cavity (notably residues like Tyr/Phe in the binding region), which **increases risk**.",
